{"id": "1415235028295749653", "channel_id": "1414676585772093622", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "Thank you all, I have already conveyed your latest discussions.\nI assure you that we place great emphasis on your reading experience, have been actively listening to your feedback, and are constantly working to optimize it for easier reading. Our changes to the text display format have undergone thorough research and consideration, taking into account text lengths and reading experiences across different languages. However, based on your feedback, we have realized that scrolling reading does indeed cause some inconvenience. We sincerely apologize for this.\nWe are currently developing solutions and will need some time to validate them. Thank you for your understanding and support.", "timestamp": "2025-09-10T07:18:44.541000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414676585772093622", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Dialogue Scroll Was a Mistake", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1415313363319259247", "channel_id": "1415313363319259247", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "So, on steam version of the game, at the startup screen with intro video and before you click \"enter Mythag\" to log in on your account, there was an exit button on the right, and... clicking on it somehow locks the game out of login completely?? I'm guessing the exit button wasn't supposed to appear at this step, but after the login step but still before entering Mythag to play the game. At least on phone the exit button doesn't appear at this point but after login step.\n\nWhat's even more insane is that even clicking on fix or reinstalling entirely from steam, doesn't fix it? I just can't log on steam anymore. Thankfully it still works on my phone, but now I can't record more stuffs for my next video, though I have plenty of materials to work with for now.", "timestamp": "2025-09-10T12:30:01.066000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "cry2", "emoji_id": "1356068126894194758", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1415313364447531048", "filename": "2025-09-10_14-25-25.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 16438086, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1415313363319259247/1415313364447531048/2025-09-10_14-25-25.mp4?ex=69cbbe49&is=69ca6cc9&hm=e16bacc7cf901cd63b68b989da064bd635528c4c4421d296fde656818945e74b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415313363319259247", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Steam game login bricked when hitting exit", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
