{"id": "1415454525182971974", "channel_id": "1415313363319259247", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "I guess the solution was to completely remove the folder containing Morimens on computer (most likely found at C:\\SteamLibrary\\steamapps\\common), because uninstallation leaves some leftover. I don't know why I didn't think about that sooner, because that's the only way it would still load what ever is not working with steam despite reinstallation.\n\nSo now it works on steam, however I have no clue why the issue happened", "timestamp": "2025-09-10T21:50:56.677000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1415313363319259247", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Steam game login bricked when hitting exit", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
